node.text:
Discovering underwater history in Norway, Aqaba, Egypt and Malta. Tag someone who needs to see this! 🤯 Wanna see your pictures posted in our account? Apply for a feature on nomadfervor.com (link in my bio: @nomadfervor) 

Locations:
1. S/S Frankenwald near Gulen, Norway
2, 5, 6, 7, 9, 10. Aqaba, Jordan
3. The P31 from Comino in Malta
4. The Giannis D at Abu Nuhas, Red Sea, Egypt
8. Rozi the tug boat in Ċirkewwa near the ferry terminal to Gozo, Malta.

📷 @alex_dawson_photography
